metadata.name: Sea Her
metadata.description:
The sweet sound of her melody echoed throughout the sea, catching the attention of the other sea creatures. 

As they approached, they were amazed at the sight of a beautiful mermaid playing such a beautiful instrument.

This was the first time any of them had seen or heard such a thing.

They listened in awe as the mermaid strummed away, her fingers gliding effortlessly over the strings. 

The other fish were so enchanted that they didn't even realize they were tapping their fins along to the beat. 

It was a magical moment that would forever be etched in their memories.
